[36m(TaskRunner pid=3821232)[0m                                                     'in the Observation. The '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3821232)[0m                                                     'various types of objects '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3821232)[0m                                                     'in the kitchen include\n'
